<p>Another challenge that came easy for the Lopez household was blending two families together when Jennifer began dating Alex Rodriguez.</p>

<p>He has two daughters, Natasha and Ella, from a previous marriage to Cynthia Scurtis which ended in 2008.</p>

<p>Lopez also has a son, Max, with ex-husband Marc Anthony. They ended their relationship in 2011 and were officially divorced in 2014. </p>

<p>'It was very organic. They just clicked,' she said of the four children together. 'It was just very easy.' </p>

